  "text": "Eq. (5.1a, b) is then the metric for a multicentered Taub-NUT space [CITATION_1] . The S 1 fiber shrinks over each center x I on the R 3 base. In this geometry, we obtain 2-cycles with the topology of spheres from the fibration over curves in R 3 connecting any pair of centers",
